Wizards can nuke a little slower for large amounts of damage and they can do it with fire/cold/magic.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Wizards only got the inefficient and not so large (even by magician standards) cold nuke ice comet and only the relatively rare large magic DD of Elnerich's Electrical Rending.<br>
