<br>
Quote by Wezloc:<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Wizard nukes OVERALL are superior to mage nukes in damage, cast time, ratio, mana cost.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
The ratio's can you see by my comparison of the PoP spells that its not that large.<br>
<br>
<br>
Quote by Wezloc:<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Wizard can crit without the need of AA<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Wizards gets 2% chance of getting a random 0 to 50% bonus to damage. This amounts to an impressive 0.5% average damage increase.<br>
<br>
<br>
Quote by Wezloc:<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Wizards have manaburn<br>
