Quote by Wezloc:<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Yes Fire Bolt of Tallon is 3.75 but has line of sight issues and is still weaker then Ice Spear which has no line of sight issues, cost less mana, does the same damage in less then half the time and I might add it is soon to be two expansions old.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Icespear also have 13 seconds recast time, while Firebolt of Tallon have 0. You can cast 2.75 times as many firebolts during the same time as icespears.<br>
That icespear is two expansions old does matter in what way exactly if later expansions doesnt include upgrades?<br>
<br>
<br>
